reviewText: Sleazy gore and plenty of nudity. A police station that is really just someone's living room. A reporter that looks like your friend's mom and is supposed to be attractive. Amazing!

A bunch of couples are being killed and the girl is raped. Police have only one suspect (Charles Fuller).

Bad acting, lousy script, terrible special effects. Good nudity.

Guide: F-word, sex, nudity (Mara Lynn Bastian, Temple Mead, Anita Reformado, Anne Walker, Doreen Semese)
